-sportsman-and-comeback-of-the-year-at-laureus-awards|title=Roger Federer wins Sportsman and Comeback of the Year at Laureus Awards|publisher=Sky Sports|author1=Nicholas Wright|date=27 February 2018|accessdate=27 February 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Gran Gal\u00e0 del Calcio|Gran Gal\u00e0 del Calcio AIC]] Career Award: 2018<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.asroma.com/en/news/2018/12/totti-receives-career-award-at-gran-gala-del-calcio|title=TOTTI RECEIVES CAREER AWARD AT GRAN GALA DEL CALCIO|publisher=AS Roma|date=4 December 2018|accessdate=5 February 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Italian Football Hall of Fame]]: 2018<ref name=\"2018-SerieAHoF\">{{cite web|url=https://www.figc.it/it/formazione-ed-eventi/news/totti-zanetti-e-allegri-tra-i-premiati-dell-8-edizione-della-hall-of-fame-del-calcio-italiano/|title=Totti, Zanetti e Allegri tra i premiati dell\u20198\u00aa edizione della \u2018Hall of Fame del calcio italiano\u2019|publisher=FIGC.it|language=Italian|date=19 February 2019|accessdate=20 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n[[File:Totti Champions Promenade Monaco.jpg|thumb|Totti's footprint on ''The Champions Promenade'' in [[Monaco]]]]\n\n'''Orders'''\n:[[File:Cavaliere OMRI BAR.svg|left|50px]] 5th Class / Knight: ''Cavaliere Ordine al Merito della Repubblica Italiana'': 2000<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.quirinale.it/elementi/DettaglioOnorificenze.aspx?decorato=79735|title=Cavaliere Ordine al Merito della Repubblica Italiana|date=12 July 2000|accessdate=31 May 2011|publisher=Presidenza della Repubblica|language=Italian}}</ref>\n:[[File:Friedrich Order.png|left|50px]] [[Italian National Olympic Committee|CONI]]: Golden Collar of Sports Merit: ''Collare d'Oro al Merito Sportivo'': 2006<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.coni.it/it/news/primo-piano/49-primo-piano-2006/2935-coni-_consegna_dei_collari_d&rsquo%3Boro_e_dei_diplomi_d&rsquo%3Bonore-_premia_il_presidente_del_consiglio_romano_prodi-_diretta_tv_su_rai_2.html |title=Coni: Consegna dei Collari d\u2019Oro e dei Diplomi d\u2019Onore. Premia il President